module.exports = {
  baseUrl:
    process.env.REACT_APP_NODE_ENV === "development"
      ? "http://localhost:3000/api"
      : process.env.REACT_APP_NODE_ENV === "staging"
        ? "http://51.77.211.228:3000/api"
        : process.env.REACT_APP_NODE_ENV === "test"
          ? "http://51.83.98.252:3000/api"
          : "http://localhost:3000/api",
  roleIdSuperAdmin: 1,
  roleIdAdmin: 2,
  roleIdProfessor: 3,
  roleIdParent: 4,
  roleIdStudent: 5,
  roleIdSupervisor: 6,
  roleIdDirector: 7,
  frequencyMonthly: 4,
  frequencyQuarterly: 5,
  frequencyAnnually: 7,
  unpaidInvoice: 0,
  partiallyPaidInvoice: 1,
  billPaid: 2,
  lateInvoice: 3
};
